within reach, they run away from us.

69
00:03:51,190 --> 00:03:53,300
Then it repeats.

70
00:03:54,920 --> 00:04:00,260
And when they're finally within our grasp, we get kicked down by them.

71
00:04:03,990 --> 00:04:07,230
Is this going to happen 
for our whole lives?

72
00:04:07,990 --> 00:04:08,990
Brother...

73
